WEBVTT

02:24.500 --> 02:26.458
Leave her alone.

03:22.166 --> 03:23.250
On music.

06:40.583 --> 06:41.750
...my child.

06:43.666 --> 06:45.250
What's wrong, Puleng?

06:55.875 --> 06:58.541
Or were you planning to go
without saying anything?

06:58.625 --> 07:00.250
I was going to tell you, Makhu.

14:53.208 --> 14:54.375
...about Dad's trial.

15:58.250 --> 15:59.208
No.

24:12.166 --> 24:13.583
Fikile's the side piece?

24:39.666 --> 24:44.833
How is such a simple high school story
making such waves?

24:45.583 --> 24:47.166
It's because it's Parkhurst.

24:52.291 --> 24:57.500
Oh, my heart. My baby.

25:03.250 --> 25:06.416
Don't even get me started
with that Puleng girl...

25:17.208 --> 25:19.208
Hey, what's wrong with you, young lady?

25:27.625 --> 25:29.125
No need to be hasty.

26:35.458 --> 26:36.541
Polygamy?

32:24.750 --> 32:26.333
Puleng, where have you been?

32:54.125 --> 32:55.333
Whoever broke in here...

33:04.708 --> 33:05.708
...someone unfamiliar...

38:14.916 --> 38:18.208
-You're not doing anything!
-What do you want me to do?

38:18.291 --> 38:19.625
I don't know!

41:12.750 --> 41:14.791
But what's going on, Makhu?

41:38.916 --> 41:39.916
...my child.
